CursesToolKit
Curses based general gadget toolkit

Library for creating general purpose curses based gadgets.
Written entirely in c++.

Gadgets available:
Buttons.
Text box ( scrollable).
Menubar and menuitems.
Input box.
Edit box.
Source code edit box.
List box.
Check box.
Label.
Frame buffer image.
File Chooser.

Convenience functions:
Entry dialog.
Query dialog.
Save file dialog.
Open file dialog.
Open folder dialog.
About dialog.

Main application class including event handlers etc.

Loads to do yet, see the examples for a taster.